{"tid":1869502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"T.O.P為香港發聲：唔想回歸一直過得不好","createTime":"2020-02-08T08:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T14:47:28.000Z","uid":50776,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec69620c4424f9dd73e4ec7d5ad7028cd475b858","tid":1869502,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"韓團Big Bang的32歲成員T.O.P於去年7月退伍，當兵期間爆出涉吸大麻被判緩刑的他，曾在社交網回應粉絲稱沒有復出之意，但所屬YG事務所早前卻宣布Big Bang將於4月參加美國加州舉行的科契拉音樂節（The Coachella Valley Music and Arts Festival），惹起不少網民反感。<br />\n不時在IG晒美術照的T.O.P昨晚突然開直播與粉絲分享近況，一臉憔悴的他架着眼鏡兼頭髮凌亂，更帶醉意透露開直播原因：「只係想向大家展示我過得點樣，我覺得大家都唔知道，其實我經常對粉絲們感到好抱歉！」他又強調：「我冇打算喺韓國展開活動，我根本都唔想回歸，對於冇任何想法嘅人，拜託，唔好再有相關報道啦，啲人真係好壞！」<br />\n期間有粉絲在直播中問他近況，T.O.P透露最近正錄製音樂，又不斷重覆說：「我過得唔好，唔係咁好，一直都過得唔好！」有粉絲對於T.O.P的狀況大表擔心，希望其家人與朋友可以好好開導他，但繼續有大批網民炮轟他不應飲醉酒開直播，並批評他不想回歸之言論過於輕率，完全沒有考慮隊友與粉絲的心情。"},{"pid":"4f125f2c6d71fb4f393f06b4243bfbfa57d8b9fa","tid":1869502,"uid":78773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:20:48.000Z","msg":"屌，睇曬成篇文都搵唔到香港兩隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗"},{"pid":"3129d1167f3ef3177fad4c375e8b2d11db270ee2","tid":1869502,"uid":236011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:27:00.000Z","msg":"邊忽講香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecec0ff3ced342258363898517497b346142adf4","tid":1869502,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f125f2c6d71fb4f393f06b4243bfbfa57d8b9fa","tid":1869502,"uid":78773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:20:48.000Z","msg":"屌，睇曬成篇文都搵唔到香港兩隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"Clickbait<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4046ca890e3a51be9e3867aca4d192ff245a0311","tid":1869502,"uid":211317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T10:03:11.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f173fdd6b13ecd42baa99dcda4925c48188d26d3","tid":1869502,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b3a2f984f45af26c092cfba4d5ae108ebceb8e","tid":1869502,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}